---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="bg-gray-900 text-gray-300 py-12 mt-auto">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
    <div class="md:col-span-1">
      <a href="/" class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-white mb-4 block">
        AKA<span class="text-blue-500">Software</span>
      </a>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
        AI ve modern yazılım teknolojileriyle işletmenizin dijital dönüşümüne rehberlik ediyoruz.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div>
      <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-4">Hızlı Bağlantılar</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
        <li><a href="/hizmetler" class="hover:text-blue-400">Hizmetler</a></li>
        <li><a href="/vaka-calismalari" class="hover:text-blue-400">Vaka Çalışmaları</a></li>
        <li><a href="/blog" class="hover:text-blue-400">Blog</a></li>
        <li><a href="/hakkimizda" class="hover:text-blue-400">Hakkımızda</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div>
